<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240923/1727074313560068624.jpg" title="1727074313560068624.jpg" alt="5199496d5cf20c198f470db3a451876.jpg"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">江软经管分院祝愿各位2024级江软学子</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">在今后的大学生活里</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">能够学有所成</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">勇攀高峰</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">收获满满</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">用汗水和努力书写属于自己的辉煌篇章</span></p><p><br/></p>